<subSubSection id="C32ADAB5FFFF0F5BFF3BFE99CD39FE1C" pageId="13" pageNumber="196" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="8B8F893EFFFF0F5BFF3BFE99CD39FE1C" blockId="13.[169,1376,294,529]" pageId="13" pageNumber="196">
<emphasis id="B944552CFFFF0F5BFF3BFE99CE7EFEE4" bold="true" box="[171,523,294,327]" pageId="13" pageNumber="196">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. The Forest Giant Pouched Rat is hunted extensively for food over much of its distribution. Despitethis pressure,it does not appear to have a contracted distribution or reduced population.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
